Mesopotamian night is an
organization that tries to have

01:33:12.060 --> 01:33:15.830
through sheer voluntary
activity, Assyrian events

01:33:15.830 --> 01:33:21.050
that include both popular
and new music.

01:33:21.050 --> 01:33:25.810
Mesopotamian night draws
on the works of people

01:33:25.810 --> 01:33:28.800
