01:34:15.180 --> 01:34:20.440
But the future direction,
my particular interest

01:34:20.440 --> 01:34:24.230
over the next few years is in
the Assyrian Arts Institute.

01:34:24.230 --> 01:34:28.000
A new organization which
is very, very different

01:34:28.000 --> 01:34:31.070
from the older organizations
because it is committed

01:34:31.070 --> 01:34:35.820
to being an institutionalized
endowed structure,

01:34:35.820 --> 01:34:38.230
endowed is the key word.

01:34:38.230 --> 01:34:43.810
And the commitment is to promoting
language, promoting awareness

01:34:43.810 --> 01:34:47.500
of Assyrian arts and
promoting performance.

01:34:47.500 --> 01:34:53.500
Other promising directions, there
